            </span>
            <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: #7f1d1d; border: 1px solid #7f1d1d; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">
              <span style="width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 999px; background: #fca5a5;"></span>
